Objective: to implement a slider with promotional items on the main page
Solution:
    1) The poster application was created
    2) We created Poster model
    3) We created a template_tag to retrieve Poster objects from the database
    4) Created a template with poster visual and used template_tag
        from step 3
    5) Template from the 4th step was used in the main page template and
        wanted it could be used in any place
    6) You can add a product to the poster through the admin panel for this
        purpose was created InLine view for the admin panel